# Keep host-side artifacts out of image build contexts (context = repo root).
# Without this, COPY services/frontend/ ./ overwrites the image's freshly
# npm-installed node_modules with the host's (macOS) one and vite breaks.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/__pycache__
.git
.env
tls
backups
web-search-mcp
.claude
